{"title": "Foreign Re-Score", "content": "For whatever reason, be it legal issues or Creative Differences, a work gets completely re-scored when being released outside its country of origin. These may or may not happen with a bonus serving of No Export for You for the original soundtrack (and in some cases, the new soundtrack as well).\n\nIf the original music was done by a separate band (not in-house), then an entire separate license needs to be drawn up for the music, apart from the work itself. In some cases, the band may flat-out refuse, or they may demand huge royalties that would double the expense of porting the work.", "url": "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ForeignReScore", "media_links": ["/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/FourKidsEntertainment", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Anime/Pokemon", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Anime/SonicX", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/SonicAdventure2", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Anime/Pokemon", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Anime/CastleInTheSky", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/Disney", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Anime/TheMysteriousCitiesOfGold", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Anime/DragonBallZ", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/Digimon", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/DiC", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Manga/SailorMoon", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Anime/TheVisionOfEscaflowne", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/ToyStory2", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/SchindlersList", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/TheRaid", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/GoneWithTheWind", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/TheNeverendingStory", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/HogansHeroes", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Theatre/ShowBoat", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/SonicTheHedgehogCD", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/GuiltyGear", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/Shinobi", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/MegaMan", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/MegaMan8", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/MegaManX3", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/MegaManX5", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/MegaManX2", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/Activision", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/BioMetal", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.